{
  "doc": "4-agent delegation chain demo — Processor (C) is missing 'grants'.\n\nChain: Reporter (A) → Analyzer (B) → Processor (C) → Writer (D)\n\nWriter (D) still holds FS:write_file with delegation='explicit'.\nProcessor (C) forgot to declare 'grants', so when check_program() inspects\nthe C→D call it raises FC-E010 (ExplicitDelegationViolation).\n\nZone of Indifference: without 'grants' enforcement, irreversible filesystem\naccess could silently flow from D up through C to any caller of C.",
  "nail": "0.9.0",
  "kind": "delegation-chain",
  "defs": [
    {
      "op": "def",
      "name": "write_output",
      "doc": "Writer (D) — owns FS:write_file with explicit delegation.",
      "effects": {
        "allow": [
          {
            "op": "FS:write_file",
            "reversible": false,
            "delegation": "explicit"
          }
        ]
      },
      "grants": ["FS:write_file"],
      "body": []
    },
    {
      "op": "def",
      "name": "run_pipeline",
      "doc": "Processor (C) — forgot to add 'grants': ['FS:write_file']. FC-E010 fires here.",
      "effects": {
        "allow": [
          {
            "op": "FS:write_file",
            "reversible": false,
            "delegation": "explicit"
          }
        ]
      },
      "body": [
        {"op": "call", "fn": "write_output"}
      ]
    },
    {
      "op": "def",
      "name": "generate_report",
      "doc": "Analyzer (B) — properly declares grants.",
      "effects": {
        "allow": [
          {
            "op": "FS:write_file",
            "reversible": false,
            "delegation": "explicit"
          }
        ]
      },
      "grants": ["FS:write_file"],
      "body": [
        {"op": "call", "fn": "run_pipeline"}
      ]
    },
    {
      "op": "def",
      "name": "write_summary",
      "doc": "Reporter (A) — properly declares grants.",
      "effects": {
        "allow": [
          {
            "op": "FS:write_file",
            "reversible": false,
            "delegation": "explicit"
          }
        ]
      },
      "grants": ["FS:write_file"],
      "body": [
        {"op": "call", "fn": "generate_report"}
      ]
    }
  ]
}
